content: This is one of the most useful apps I have ever used.

I'm really enjoying playing with this app. I paint in watercolors and it's fun to take pics and give them a watercolor treatment. There are several prefixed filters or you can forgo those and do the adjustments manually. I only wish there was an option to add bleeds and back wash touches.
Love this! Great for craft projects!!
Finally! A real watercolor app for Android!! Thank you!!!
Great watetcolor versatility, easy to use
Very nice app. I think it would be easier to use for longer periods if there was a save button that is always on screen. Rather than having to press home then save.
This app allows a great deal of creativity within the preset parameters it provides. I've always been happy using the developers' photo apps!
Great App! Versatile, easy to use app with a wide variety of options and the ability to customize specific effects.

My first experiance and l love it. Can play with color and details. Not so great with faces if you want realism but you have a photograph for that. Love the painterly effects and representational abstract you can control.
Effects are very limited, I bought the app thinking I would get more but got just the same..so many free apps. with a larger variety out there.
Best water color app I've found for android phones.
This app makes your photos look so cool. You could pay someone on Etsy to do this, or you could do it yourself and customize it to look exactly how you want. 10/10 would buy again.
i love jixipix i use bluristic a lot, but most paint filter don't go well together with photos from bluristic, and wirh this app work perfectly. thanks!
